casebody.data:
Edward MORGAN
v.
Darrel VANNOY, Warden Louisiana State Penitentiary NO. 2018-KH-0935 Supreme Court of Louisiana. April 8, 2019

Denied. Applicant has previously exhausted his right to state collateral review and fails to show that any exception permits his successive filing. See *612State ex rel. Morgan v. State, 16-0471 (La.6/16/17), 221 So.3d 838.
